records.description: A fairly large storage system that utilizes a parallel unloading array allowing the system to unload at a max of 8x hopper speed.
features: Has various peripherals: restock stations, furnace array, crafting station, and yeeting station, masscrafter, brewer, and unstackable sorter
Has a concrete duper in the middle of the storage (This was requested, can easily be omitted in the building process)
Has a big bulk with capacity for ~1.3m / item.
Has 1 DC capacity chest halls with SS2 filters.
considerations: This system requires you to have Carpet's `stackableShulkerBoxes` rule enabled and subsequently Kikugie's StackableShulkerFix.
records.notes:
Tested for ~400k items without issues
